    "data": [
        [
            [
                "NO"
            ],
            [
                "Two and a half weeks had already passed ever since my first encounter with [Paul]."
            ],
            [
                "And in that time, we've had so much fun."
            ],
            [
                "I got to know [Paul] more, and we played so many games, along with doing work together and"
            ],
            [
                "discovering we actually make a very good team."
            ],
            [
                "As of now, [Paul] and I are writing in our notebooks."
            ],
            [
                "The day would’ve been a very boring one if it weren't for [Paul], who looks nervous every time I look at [him]."
            ],
            [
                "I feel like [he] wants to tell me something…"
            ],
            [
                "U-um… [tn]? "
            ],
            [
                "Yeah? "
            ],
            [
                "Are you… free by any chance today?"
            ],
            [
                "Sure, I don’t have anything to do after class, why?"
            ],
            [
                "Okay! Just- just to know."
            ],
            [
                "A-ha! I knew it."
            ],
            [
                "And with that, [Paul] turns and resumes working on [his] notebook once more."
            ],
            [
                "I do so as well, but can’t hide the shy smile on my face."
            ],
            [
                "The bell rings once more and I stretch out of my place."
            ],
            [
                "Allriiiight, let’s go to the park."
            ],
            [
                "Actually, I need to do something before that…"
            ],
            [
                "How about we meet there in an hour?"
            ],
            [
                "Oh. Okay! No worries, see you then."
            ],
            [
                "[Paul] waved at me goodbye and took off faster than a hedgehog."
            ],
            [
                "I opted to spend my time under one of the many trees in my school, excited about seeing [Paul] again."
            ],
            [
                "I didn’t want to admit it, but [Paul] really made my days brighter."
            ],
            [
                "[He] was always there, and made me smile each and every time we spoke."
            ],
            [
                "[His] beautiful smile, [his] patience, and the way [he] always wanted to be with me…"
            ],
            [
                "My mind wanders, and all I could think about were [Paul]'s lips."
            ],
            [
                "They were so nice and round, probably soft too, and-"
            ],
            [
                "WHAT AM I THINKING???"
            ],
            [
                "My heart beats with force as I shake my head once more. "
            ],
            [
                "It was hard to admit, but I can just wonder… Why did I think about [Paul] like that?"
            ],
            [
                "Am I… catching feelings for [him]?"
            ],
            [
                "I look at my clock and 45 minutes had passed."
            ],
            [
                "I guess it’s time for me to move my booty and get going."
            ],
            [
                "I look at the sky and let myself forget my thoughts from earlier."
            ],
            [
                "Nothing like that is gonna happen today, [tn]. Forget about it!"
            ],
            [
                "The sun shines as I arrive there and begin looking for [Paul]."
            ],
            [
                "The park is filled with beautiful and tall trees, with a lot of places to go sit and relax."
            ],
            [
                "Maybe it would have been nice to meet up in a specific place, but oh well."
            ],
            [
                "I look around, trying to figure out where [Paul] could be."
            ],
            [
                "When suddenly, I feel two hands grab me by the shoulders."
            ],
            [
                "Boo!"
            ],
            [
                "AAAAAH!!!!"
            ],
            [
                "I turn around and just find [Paul]'s cheeky grin, smiling at me. "
            ],
            [
                "Hahaha! Look at your face! I wish I had a camera on me right now."
            ],
            [
                "I roll my eyes, but still find myself chuckling at the joke. "
            ],
            [
                "Welp, I’m glad you could make it."
            ],
            [
                "I’ve actually got something prepared for you. So… let’s get walking."
            ],
            [
                "As we walk, we enjoy a comfortable silence."
            ],
            [
                "Suddenly, I remembered something I had been meaning to ask [Paul] for quite some time,"
            ],
            [
                "and this was the perfect opportunity to do so."
            ],
            [
                "So, [Paul], I never had the chance to ask you…"
            ]
        ],
